#: ../../manual/getting_started/configuration/hardware.rst:107
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"3D mice or :abbr:`NDOF (N-Degrees of Freedom)` devices are hardware that "
"you can use to navigate a scene in Blender. Currently only devices made "
"by 3Dconnexion are supported. These devices allow you to explore a scene,"
" as well as :ref:`Fly/Walk modes <3dview-fly-walk>`."
msgstr ""
"Los ratones 3D o dispositivos de :abbr:`NDOF *(N-Degrees of Freedom)* "
"(N-Grados de Libertad)` son hardware que puede utilizar para navegar en "
"una escena de Blender. Actualmente sólo se soportan dispositivos creados "
"por '3dconnexion'. Estos dispositivos le permiten explorar una escena, "
"así como también utilizar los :ref:`modos Caminar/Volar <3dview-"
"walk_fly>`."

